reviewText: I first heard of Jenna Jameson when she was in a Cheri magazine in 1994.  I wasn't really that impressed with her.  She went on to probably become the biggest porn star of all time.  This dvd is not all that great either.  It has her on the cover but she doesn't do much.  It features some other girls who I have never heard of doing lap dances.  Once I watched this I have never watched it again.  As I get older I am less into this kind of stuff.
